<note n="0912005" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0912005">釋【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0912006" resp="#resp1" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0912006">惟【大】，唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
